<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewdivort"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta httdiv-equiv="X-UA-Comdivatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/result.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/footer.css">
    <title>Result</title>
</head>

<body>

<div>
    <ul class="middle_head">
        <li>
            <div class="content_h1">{{userEntity.getId}} 님의 한줄요약입니다.
            </div>
            <div class="content_h1">
                BMI 는 {{bmi}},
                한국 {{sex}} 평균 {{average}}% 입니다.
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="main">
    <ul class="main_section">
        <li class="main_left_1">
            <h2>현재 운동량</h2>
            <div class="main_in" name="cal">
                <div class="content_small">{{result}} kcal.</div>
            </div>
            <h2>현재 사용자 정보</h2>
            <div class="main_left_in">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content_mid">사용자 :</div>
                        <div class="content_bold">{{userEntity.getId}}</div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content_mid">키 (cm) :</div>
                        <div class="content_bold"> {{userEntity.getHeight}}</div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content_mid">몸무게 (kg) :</div>
                        <div class="content_bold"> {{userEntity.getWeight}}</div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content_mid">bmi :</div>
                        <div class="content_bold">{{bmi}} / {{bmis}}</div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="main_right">
            <h2>운동한 시간동안 어떤 걸 할 수 있을까?</h2>

            <div class="main_in">
                <div class="content_small">당신이 살려준 닭은 {{chicken}}마리</div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <div class="main_in">
                <div class="content_small">택시를 타면 {{taxi}}원 정도 시간?</div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <div class="main_in">
                <div class="content_small">영화를 보면 평균 {{movie}}편 시청.</div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <div class="main_in">
                <div class="content_small">최저시급으로 따지면 {{pay}}원!</div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <div class="main_in">
                <div class="content_small"> 노래를 들으면 {{music}}곡 청취.</div>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="button">
        <button type="button"><a href="/calculator">다시하기</a></button>
        <button type="button"><a href="/secondhome">홈으로</a></button>
    </div>
</div>
{{>footer}}
</body>

</html>